{"tid":927353,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港咁靚但咁多人想破壞佢","createTime":"2018-12-04T06:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T11:11:53.000Z","uid":47170,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3012f1bd53aef6f134c39cde63bf1891be0d1ed8","tid":927353,"uid":47170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"唔知擺咩台好 先擺創意台<br />\n<br />\n今日搭搭下車望出窗外<br />\n突然覺得香港好靚<br />\n但總係有啲人不斷破壞香港<br />\n唔係只講政治上嘅破壞<br />\n仲有啲人毫無公民意識 <br />\n打尖 貪小便宜 隨地吐痰 唔識尊重人etc<br />\n一啲咁小嘅事都做唔好<br />\n點解仲要繼續留係呢個地方<br />\n每一個嚟香港嘅人都係想榨乾呢到嘅一切<br />\n然後轉身離開<br />\n<br />\n諗到咁就會好感概<br />\n一啲小事都做唔好 仲講咩做大事啊"},{"pid":"98715e9408d51d48970feac9698bfc6b44aa981e","tid":927353,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2975043a289a05ab19976798422825d913157026","tid":927353,"uid":77569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e1e611a9ca263315d57136e6af101464caa8d19","tid":927353,"uid":133977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得講照香港同日本都差唔多<br />\n分別只係毒霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aede648a3d110845051c7f8fc6a4b1617b0cf56","tid":927353,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1e611a9ca263315d57136e6af101464caa8d19","tid":927353,"uid":133977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得講照香港同日本都差唔多<br />\n分別只係毒霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"景"},{"pid":"fb48c4c2d4af68e75254a9c6187a4c4c7abd2f0f","tid":927353,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"嘩 你終於醒啦！"},{"pid":"462ef8f101b59116ecc833e2036e42e1c043a3ca","tid":927353,"uid":180560,"like":1,"dislike